snippet.textDisplay: Coke studio was supposed to set benchmarks and promote and revive Pakistan's unparalleled Music Industry and creativity. That platform was supposed to be productive and present Pakistan in an unparalleled way to the world. But here, the mockery is being made out of this important platform by ruining Pakistan's great songs  sung by legendary people who carved their name over our Music Industry board and achieved milestones through hardwork. Please stop ruining this platform with such ridiculous featurings. After 1990's MCC, we get Coke Studio now only for it to be misused like this. Rohail hayaat must take charge again.
